ol.li:
(1) Confirmation of suppression of sedimentation of the solder powder;

In the embodiment 1, there was no sign such that the solder powder was settled;

In the comparison example 1, the solder powder was settled and the flux steeped from the paste surface; and

In the comparison example 2, there was no sign such that the solder powder was settled.

(2) Confirmation of Reflow Performance;

In the embodiment 1, no residue of flux remained. The solder covered whole surface of the Ni plating pattern;

In the comparison example 1, no residue of flux remained. The solder was rejected on a part of the Ni plating pattern but indicated the wettability in 50% of an area of the pattern; and

In the comparison example 2, no residue of flux remained. The solder was completely rejected on the Ni plating pattern and indicated the wettability in only 30% of an area of the pattern.

(2) Confirmation of Reflow Performance;

In the embodiment 2, no residue of flux remained. The solder covered whole surface of the Ni plating pattern; and

In the comparison example 3, white residue of flux was detected with naked eye. On the other hand, the solder covered whole surface of the Ni plating pattern. When reflowing a test piece three times, the white residue of flux then disappeared.
